text: Castelnau-d'Auzan-Labarrère is a commune in the Gers department. It is in southwestern France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Castelnau-d'Auzan (the seat) and Labarrère.Arrêté préfectoral 8 December 2015 == Related pages == * Communes of the Gers department == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Gers
